This paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques to remove highlights from a single image. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves some graphics techniques, such as dichromatic models, which could place it in the cs.GR (Graphics) category. Additionally, the paper mentions clustering and mapping techniques, which could place it in the cs.MM (Multimedia) category. The paper also involves some machine learning techniques, such as the pure diffuse pixels distribution rule, which could place it in the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) categories.
